- Produce TIFF figures (Fig1.tif etc.) in 
  /home/antagomir/proj/Science13/2014-NatComm-FinalFigures/main.R

- Add text and labels in ODG files (soffice) on top of the 
  TIF; export as Fig1.pdf with >300DPI

- Open Fig1.pdf in GIMP; crop to final figure and resize to
  85mm/180mm & >300DPI if needed;  

- Export Final Figure: Figure-1-Lahti.jpg

